getTriggers

protected static java.util.ArrayList getTriggers(Context context,
                                                 java.lang.String sTriggerString,
                                                 java.lang.String sInherited)
                                          throws FrameworkException
Returns list of triggers by processing the given result trigger string. This method uses getTriggerInFormat() method to get the list in proper format.

Parameters:
context - the eMatrix Context object
sTriggerString - - Contains result trigger chunk.
sInherited - - Contains 'Yes' if the trigger is inherited otherwise 'No'.
Returns:
ArrayList list of triggers from the given result trigger string chunk
Throws:
FrameworkException - if the operation fails
Since:
AEF 10.7

extractTriggerChunk

protected static java.util.ArrayList extractTriggerChunk(Context context,
                                                         java.lang.String sAdminObjectType,
                                                         java.lang.String sAdminObjectName)
                                                  throws FrameworkException
It runs MQL command "print < sAdminObjectType> < sAdminObjectName >" to get the list of Triggers chunk associated with the selected Admin Type. It also returns the inherited trigger chunk if exists.

Parameters:
context - the eMatrix Context object
sAdminObjectType - - Name of the Admin Object Type selected
sAdminObjectName - - Name of the Admin Object Name selected
Returns:
ArrayList which contains the list of Triggers chunk.
Throws:
FrameworkException - if the operation fails
Since:
AEF 10.7 Updated for Selectables
